The BorderContainer is a versatile Dojo layout widget, useful for arranging the main views of an application.
Dojo Campus page: http://docs.dojocampus.org/dijit/layout/BorderContainer

Check out the sample to see a functioning page that uses the BorderContainer.
Then go to the exercise page and do the following;

1. Add a new BorderContainer inside the contentpane 'cp2'
3. Add three new Contentpanes to the new BorderContainer


